com.sensorstack.provenancelayer

Class Timestamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sensorstack.provenancelayer.Timestamp

  • public class Timestamp
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates parameters for defining a timestamp. Date is depicted in "dd-MM-yyyy" format while time is depicted in "hh:mm:ss a z" format.
